title: Ezekiel Elliott, Cowboys agree to 6-year extension - Emergency Podcast (Football 9/4)
description:
The Pick Six podcast crew issues their immediate reactions to Ezekiel Elliott's record-setting deal and what it means for the Cowboys both on and off the field. The guys also discuss another record-setting extension for Jared Goff.
